thread.title: Jennie
thread.title_full: Maine Lobster Now reviewed by Jennie

author: Jennie
title: Jennie
text: This was a great find! I am from MA, living in Seattle. Really wanted a taste of home for the Superbowl (Go Pats!). Easy checkout, fast delivery all the way to Seattle, my 4-6 lb lobster was easily 6 lbs if not more, alive and well as promised. And delicous to boot! This won't be the last time I order from these folks. Thank you!
